/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 311.0 Tm (The pipeline under study had three broad stages: a worker processed evidence, a builder) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 297.0 Tm (composed a packet for adjudication, and a gate model returned a verdict. Observed) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 283.0 Tm (verdict variance across repeated runs raised the question of whether the variance was) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 269.0 Tm (model sampling noise or something in the input.) Tj
1 0 0 1 72.0 249.0 Tm (The investigation was not originally aimed at input hygiene. It surfaced during) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 235.0 Tm (model-portability work: we were testing whether a structured evaluation pipeline could) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 221.0 Tm (produce stable verdicts when the underlying gate model was substituted. While testing a) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 207.0 Tm (GPT-family gate model at temperature 0, we observed verdict variance that did not fit) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 193.0 Tm (the pattern we expected from model-level nondeterminism alone. The variance was) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 179.0 Tm (structured and tied to specific cases. Investigating that variance led to the) Tj
1 0 0 1 84.0 165.0 Tm (input-hygiene finding.) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
